## ğŸ“‚ Files in This Repo
- `Dockerfile` â†’ Used to create the Survey Web App container image.
- `deployment.yaml` â†’ Defines the Kubernetes Deployment.
- `service.yaml` â†’ Creates a LoadBalancer service to expose the application.
- `survey-web-app-deployment.yaml` â†’ Detailed deployment specification.
- `survey.html` â†’ The frontend of the survey app.
- `eks-trust-policy.json` â†’ IAM Trust Policy for EKS Cluster.
- `worker-node-trust-policy.json` â†’ IAM Trust Policy for Worker Nodes.

## ğŸ“Œ How to Deploy the Application
### **1ï¸âƒ£ Prerequisites**
- AWS CLI installed & configured (`aws configure`)
