- Docker installed

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Deploy on EKS**
1. **Create the EKS Cluster**
   ```sh
   aws eks create-cluster --name survey-cluster --role-arn arn:aws:iam::<ACCOUNT_ID>:role/EKS-Cluster-Role --resources-vpc-config subnetIds=<SUBNET_IDs>,securityGroupIds=<SECURITY_GROUP_ID>
